750
01:00:06,349 --> 01:00:07,475
Itu dari dia?

751
01:00:09,560 --> 01:00:10,603
Jawablah.

752
01:00:13,564 --> 01:00:14,649
Silakan.

753
01:00:20,196 --> 01:00:21,405
Bagaimana kau bisa

754
