763
01:00:52,270 --> 01:00:53,688
<i>Aku mau bicarakan sesuatu.</i>

764
01:00:54,355 --> 01:00:55,565
<i>Kapan kau selesai bekerja?</i>

765
01:00:58,442 --> 01:01:00,570
Aku bermain basket hari ini.

766
01:01:02,196 --> 01:01:04,073
<i>Kau bersama Gi-seok?</i>

767
01:01:06,826 --> 01:01:07,869
Ya.

768
01:01:09,120 --> 01:01:11,247
